import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { NgbDropdownConfig, NgbDropdownModule,NgbNavConfig,NgbNavModule } from '@ng-bootstrap/ng-bootstrap'; import { faHome } from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons'; @Component({ selector: 'app-root', templateUrl: './app.component.html', styleUrls: ['./app.component.css'] }) @Component({ selector: 'ngbd-dropdown-config', standalone: true, imports: [NgbDropdownModule], templateUrl: './app.component.html', providers: [NgbDropdownConfig], // add NgbDropdownConfig to the component providers }) @Component({ selector: 'ngbd-nav-config', standalone: true, imports: [NgbNavModule], templateUrl: './app.component.html', providers: [NgbNavConfig], // add NgbNavConfig to the component providers }) export class AppComponent { //title = 'Front-Angular'; //faHome=faHome; } export class NgbdDropdownConfig { constructor(config: NgbDropdownConfig) { // customize default values of dropdowns used by this component tree config.placement = 'top-start'; config.autoClose = false; } } export class NgbdNavConfig { constructor(config: NgbNavConfig) { // customize default values of navs used by this component tree config.destroyOnHide = false; config.roles = false; } }
